com.ephesoft.gxt.systemconfig.shared

Interface SystemConfigSharedConstants


  • public interface SystemConfigSharedConstants
    This CustomWorkflowSharedConstants class is responsible for holding the shared constants for the Custom workflow module. It includes the constants that can be shared among client and server side.
    Version:
    1.0.0

    $LastChangedRevision:$
